&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What do we need&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Protein Metrics is the leading provider of protein characterization software that allows scientists to perform highly-accurate analyses on the data generated from mass spectrometry and other analytical platforms. Our customers include 150+ biopharma companies and 300+ academic organization. Byosphere represents the latest innovation in vendor-neutral analysis software, bringing the industry-leading Byos software to the cloud with computational automation and visualization capabilities built-in.&lt;/p&gt;
